As per the Government decision dated 15.07.2024, final recognition has been granted to the new colleges for the academic year 2024-2025. However, Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar Marathwada University, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar, a university under reference No. The letter, dated 2nd March, has requested for modification in the affiliation order of the Deogiri Law College, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar, run by the Marathwada Shiksha Prasarak Board. Accordingly, the university's recommendations and documents were examined. According to the investigation, the No. As the above approval order of Deogiri Law College, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar, a law college run by Marathwada Shiksha Prasarak Board needs to be amended in the Government decision, the Government is approving the amendment mentioned in the following statement.
